        Performs a MAHMI web search against the reference/posible Blast database Search an AminoAcidSequence aligning against the MAHMI Blast database(s)
        Parameters:
        sequence - The sequence to align
        databases - The list of databases against witch to align. Accepted databases are refdb and posdb
        threshold - The Blast execution potential bioactivity threshold
        bioactivity - The list of potential bioactivities to search
        path - The temporal alignment folder
        blastOptions - The Blast execution options
        Returns:
        the list of BlastAlignments
        See Also:
        BlastOptions, AminoAcidSequence
